label: LHC5020
decription: DIN-rail module with 10 digital ouputs and 4 digital inputs
overview: This device can be used for controlling standard floor heating valves
inclusion:
1.) Set your ZWave controller in inclusion mode

2.) Press the inclusion button on the LHC5020 device three times quickly

3.) The diode will blink to confirm the inclusion is done
exclusion:
1.) Set your ZWave controller in exclusion mode

2.) Press the inclusion button on the LHC5020 device three times quickly

3.) The diode will blink to confirm the exclusion is done

Reset the device

The device can be reset by holding down the inclusion button for 10 sec.

parameters.label: Diode control
parameters.overview:
0 Turned off

1 Turned on (Default)

2 Blinking 1 sec. interval

3 Blinking 0.5 sec. interval

parameters.label: Turn on/off voltage on input terminal 1
parameters.description: Turn on/off voltage on input terminal 1
parameters.overview:
If trigger devices on the input terminal needs external power supply, then turn of the voltage on the input terminal. 

0 = Voltage off (use external power supply up to 10V)

1 = Voltage on (7.5V)

parameters.label: Turn on/off voltage on input terminal 2
parameters.description: Turn on/off voltage on input terminal 2

parameters.label: Prel. filter time on input terminals
parameters.description: Preliminary filter time on input terminals

parameters.label: Threshold for triggering input
parameters.overview: In 10x milliseconds, e.g. 5 = 50 ms, meaning that the voltage on the input terminals need to be stable for more than 50 ms behold the input is counted as activated.

parameters.label: Threshold time for triggering input
parameters.overview: Time in 10x miliseconds that an input need to be activated before it is counted as activated. E.g. 50 = 500 ms.

parameters.label: Function for input terminal 1
parameters.overview:
0 = Inactive

1 = Level controlled

2 = Back edge controlled

3 = Front edge controlled.

parameters.label: Function for input terminal 4

parameters.label: Central Scene notification
parameters.overview:
Send Central Scene notification when the 4 input terminals gets activated. 

0 = Notification off

1 = Notification on
